  Ti7 chhun-thiN e5 hit-te3 khang-te7 hia, u7 chit8-tin7 gin2-a2 ti7 chheN-chhui3 e5 chhau2-pou-a2 teh that-kiu5, thit-tho5. Ti7 ha7-thiN e5 hit-te3 khang-te7 hia, u7 chit8-koa2-a2 toa7-lang5 ti7 chit8-tiau5 ke-a2 teh siu5-chui2. Chai7 chhiu-thiN e5 hit te3 khang-te7 hia, u7 lang5 teh pang3 hong-chhoe. Chai7 tang-thiN e5 hit-te3 khang-te7 hia, tak8 sou2-chai7 long2 teh loh8-seh, u7 chit8-koa2-a2 lang5 ti7 hia teh liu-peng.
