  Sio2-iong2 khoaN3-tioh8 an2-ni, sim-koaN chin tioh8-kip, tng2 chit8-e7 sin, chiu7 beh tui3 mng5-khau2 chhiong--chhut-khi3, siuN7 beh koaN2-kin2 tng2-khi3 Sin5-liong5-ki teng2-koan5, khoaN3 beh an2-choaN2 lai5 kiu3 hiah e5 lang5. Ti7 chit e5 si5-chun7, u7 thiaN tioh8 chit8-e5 siaN-im teh hoah Sio2-iong2, kong2, "Sio2-iong2, mai3 hiah tioh8-kip." Sio2-iong2 ng3 hoat-chhut siaN-im e5 sou2-chai7 teh khoaN3, chit8 e7 hoe5 thau5, I soa3 khoaN3-tioh8 chit8 e5 sio2-khoa2-a2 u7 ni5-ki2 e5 lang5 che7 ti7 toa7-thiaN--nih8, sui-jian5 khoaN3 pan7-se3, lang5 si7 chin ho5-khi3, bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 phaiN2-lang5 e5 khoan2, m7-ku2 i ia7 si7 hou7 Sio2-iong2 chhoah chit8 tio5--lah. Sio2-iong2 hoah kong2, "Li2 si7 sim2-mih8 lang5, goa2 kun-pun2 chiu7 m7-bat--li2, li2 na2 e7 chai-iaN2 goa2 e5 mia5 kio3 cho3 Sio2-iong2--leh?" Sio2-iong2 iong7 chiok giau5-gi5 e5 khau2-khi3 teh mng7--i.
  "Goa2 si7 chia e5 chu2-lang5, mia5 kio3 Ong5-tan, goa2 m7-na7 chai-iaN2 li2 e5 mia5 kio3 choe3 Sio2-iong2, goa2 ma7 chai-iaN2 li2 si7 Lim5 phok-su7 e5 hau7-siN, ti7 hu3-kin7 e5 chit8-e5 sio2-to2 teh tou7-ka2." Hit e5 lang5 chiu7 an2-ni lu3-lu3-kio3, kong2 kau3 chit8-koaN7 na2 bah-chang3 kang7-khoan2. 
  Sio2-iong2 thiaN Ong5-tan kong2 soah, chiu7 chin tioh8-kip kong2, “chit-ma2 kiu3-lang5 khah iau3-kin2, bo5 ai3 koh kap li2 ke kong2 hiah-nih8 che7.” Kong2 soah, chiu7 koh ui3 mng5-khau2 chhiong--chhut-khi3. "Tong-jian5! Kiu3-lang5 si7 chin iau3-kin2, goa2 tu2-chiah kiam2 m7-si7 u7 phai3 lang5 khi3--lah? Li2 koh ka7 tian7-si7 phah-khui khoaN3-mai7--leh," Ong5-tan chhio3-chhio3-a2 teh kong2. 
