  Ti7 chheh-pang5--nih8, Ong5-tan ka7 Sio2-iong2 kong2 chit8-e5 bo5 lang5 thiaN--koe3 e5 kou3-su7, chit-ma2 Ong5-tan chiu7 khai-si2 kong2 khi2, "Ti7 chin cha2 i2-cheng5, goa2 e5 chou2-sian si7 toa3 ti7 Tiong-in3-poan3-to2 e5 chit8-e5 chin bi2-le7 e5 sou2-chai7, in se3-tai7 long2 teh cho3-sit, seng-oah8 koe3 liau2 chin khoai3-lok8. Au7--lai5 in-ui7 cheng3-hu2 bo5-ho2, piN3 kau3 tai7-ke long2 beh bo5 png7 thang chiah8--lah. Goa2 e5 chou2-sian chiu7 thau-thau-a2 che7 chit8 chiah sio2 khi3-chun5, siuN7 beh li7-khui to5-pi7 chit-e5 khun3-khou2 e5 seng-oah8, kau3 pat8-kok khi3. Chiu7 che7 chun5 lai5 kau3 Thai3-peng5-iuN5, soa3 gu7 tioh8 toa7 hong-eng2, chun5 peng2--koe3-khi3. Ti7 tai7-ke long2 kiong5 beh hou7 im--si2 e5 si5-chun7, thiN-teng2 keng3-jian5 chhut-hian7 chit8-chiah kho-hak8-chun5, chiu7 si7 lin2 sou2 kong2 e5 put-beng5 hui-heng5 but8-the2, ka7 hiah e5 lan7-bin5 kiu3--khi2-lai5. In chai-iaN2 goa2 e5 chou2-sian bo5 hoat-tou7 ti7 ka-ki7 e5 kok-ka koh seng-oah8--loh8-khi3, chiu7 mng7 in u7 siuN7 beh khi3 khoai3-lok8 chheN-kiu5--bo5? Goa2 e5 chou2-sian sim-lai7 chiok chheng-chho2, chiu7 sng3 in e7-tang3 to5-lan7 khi3 pat8 e5 kok-ka, ma7 bo5 it-teng7 e7-tang3 hong5 siu-liu5, kin-a2-jit8 u7 chit-e5 ki-hoe7, che chin-chiaN3 si7 kiu5-chi-put-tek e5 tai7-chi3. Goa2 e5 chou2-sian chiu7 che7 kho-hak8-chun5 lai5 kau3 khoai3-lok8 chheN-kiu5, seng-oah8 koe3 kau3 chin khoai3-lok8. M7-ku2 in peng3 bo5 be7-ki3--tit, ti7 te7-kiu5 siong7, iau2-ku2 u7 chin che7 siu7-khou2 siu7-lan7 e5 jin5-lui7. Sou2-i2 in bat chiu3-choa7, lip8-ha7 chit8-e5 sin3-tiau5, chiu7-si7 in e5 au7-tai7, mui2 chit8 e5 lang5 ti7 i e5 it-seng tiong, it-teng7 ai3 lai5 te7-kiu5 chit8-pai2, ui7 tioh8 beh kiu3 ti7 hai2-siong7 gu7-lan7 e5 lan7-bin5. Goa2 u7 chit8-tiam2-a2 khah bo5 kang7-khoan2--e5, chiu7-si7 goa2 chit-ma2 teh sia2 chit8-pun2 iu2-koan te7-kiu5 bun5-beng5 e5 chheh, sou2-i2 ai3 tiam3 ti7 te7-kiu5 e5 si5-kan khah tng5, goa2 chiu7 ka7 kho-hak8-chun5 sai2 kau3 hai2-te2. Kin-a2-jit8 si7 goa2 lau5 ti7 te7-kiu5 siong7-boe2-a2 chit8-kang, bin5-a2-chai3 goa2 chiu7 beh poe tng2-khi3 khoai3-lok8 chheN-kiu5--lah. Pun2-lai5, hia m7-goan7 toe3 goan2 khi3 khoai3-lok8 chheN-kiu5 e5 lan7-bin5, goan2 long2 oe7 hou7 in chiah8 chit8-chiong2 bong7-hun5-ioh8, hou7 in pang3 be7 ki3 hit kui2 kang sou2 hoat-seng e5 tai7-chi3. M7-ku2 goa2 bo5 siuN7 beh hou7 li2 chiah8-ioh8, in-ui7 goa2 hi-bang7 li2 e7-tang3 ka7 sou2 khoaN3--tioh8 e5 tai7-chi3, toa3 tng2-khi3 te7-kiu5, kong2 hou7 lang5 chai, an2-ni te7-kiu5-lang5 chiu7 u7 hoat-tou7 chai-iaN2, iau2-ku2 u7 chit8-e5 pi2 te7-kiu5 koh khah bun5-beng5 e5 chheN-kiu5, che ma7 si7 chit8-chan5 chin ho2 e5 tai7-chi3. Ng3-bang7 te7-kiu5-lang5 i2-au7 long2 e7-tang3 ka7 kho-hak8 gian2-kiu3 khng3 ti7 thai3-khong su7-giap8 teng2, m7-thang koh kui-jit8 ti7 hia teh hoat-beng5 chit8-koa2-a2 e7 thai5-lang5 e5 bu2-khi3." 
  Sio2-iong2 thiaN Ong5-tan kong2 soah, chiok kam2-tong7 chiap loh8-khi3 kong2, “Ong5-tan a-Chek, chhiaN2 li2 hong3-sim, goa2 tng2--khi3 liau2-au7, it-teng7 oe7 ka7 kin-a2-jit8 sou2 hoat-seng kap sou2 keng-lek8 e5 tai7-chi3, chit8-sian2-gou7-li5 long2 kong2 hou7 goa2 e5 lau7-pe7 chai, chhiaN2 i chiah koh hong3-sang3 hou7 tai7-ke chai, goa2 teh siuN7, na7-si7 e7-tang3 ui3 goa2 e5 lau7-pe7 e5 chhui3 kong2 chhut chit e5 su7-sit8 e5 loe7-iong5, te7-kiu5-lang5 tai7-khai3 e7 siong-sin3 chiah tioh8.”
